headline: Royal Caribbean (RCL): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q2 Earnings?
summary: The past six months have been a windfall for Royal Caribbean’s shareholders. The company’s stock price has jumped 41.5%, hitting $345.49 per share. This run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
